##########################################
#         PHP/Base64 Encoder 1.1         #
# A script that will encode any binary   #
# file into a self-extracting php.       #
##########################################

Usage: phpbase64.rb [options] filename

Example: phpbase64.rb -o selfextractor.php program.exe

CHANGELOG

Version 1.1 
Added two more options: -x will automatically execute the extracted file, -v puts the php script in verbose mode

Version 1.0 
Initial release